/#
 The specification of how market disruption events will be represented.
 #/
enum FpML5.reporting.MarketDisruptionEventsEnum {
    # Market Disruption Events are applicable.
    Applicable 
    # Market Disruption Events are not applicable.
    NotApplicable 
    # The Market Disruption Event(s) are determined by reference to the relevant Master Agreement.
    AsSpecifiedInMasterAgreement 
    # The Market Disruption Event(s) are determined by reference to the relevant Confirmation.
    AsSpecifiedInConfirmation 

}

NotApplicable.Doc: Market Disruption Events are not applicable.
NotApplicable.Name: NotApplicable

AsSpecifiedInMasterAgreement.Doc: The Market Disruption Event(s) are determined by reference to the relevant Master Agreement.
AsSpecifiedInMasterAgreement.Name: AsSpecifiedInMasterAgreement

AsSpecifiedInConfirmation.Doc: The Market Disruption Event(s) are determined by reference to the relevant Confirmation.
AsSpecifiedInConfirmation.Name: AsSpecifiedInConfirmation
